thread.title: Paul Miller
thread.title_full: Spa Store Australia reviewed by Paul Miller

author: Paul Miller
title: Paul Miller
text: I found the Spa Store using Google, while looking for replacement spa filter cartridges. I was pleased to find they had the full set of three cartridges for my Vortex spa as a bundle deal and at a reasonable price. The online transaction process was simple. Shipping time was a little slower than expected but still ok. The cartridges arrived well packed and have given the spa a new lease on life, with improved jet pressure and the ozone generator bubbles are back to full force. I guess I should have replaced them about one year sooner. :-)
